Apple Stock Data Demo (AI-Ready Dataset)
Copyright 2025 Stavroula Agourou (github.com/staaaavv)

This project demonstrates data collection, cleaning, feature engineering, 
visualization, and reporting for the Apple Inc. (AAPL) stock using public data.

Data Sources:
- Yahoo Finance API via the `yfinance` library
- Technical indicators via the `ta` library
- PDF generation via the `reportlab` library
All mentioned libraries are open-source and used under their respective licenses.

Notes:
- All financial data are publicly available from Yahoo Finance and used only for 
  educational and demonstration purposes.
- No personal, confidential, or private data are collected or stored.
- The data, reports, and scripts provided in this repository are not intended for 
  commercial financial use or investment decisions.
- The author disclaims any responsibility for errors, omissions, or outcomes resulting 
  from the use of this material.

